intent.user_query: Which products have the most open service tickets?

phases.goal: Execute SQL query on fitness_db: SELECT p.ProductName, COUNT(st.TicketID) AS OpenTicketCount FROM fitness_db.ServiceTickets st JOIN fitness_db.Products p ON st.ProductID = p.ProductID WHERE st.Status = 'Open' GROUP BY p.ProductName ORDER BY OpenTicketCount DESC;

arguments.sql: SELECT p.ProductName, COUNT(st.TicketID) AS OpenTicketCount FROM fitness_db.ServiceTickets st JOIN fitness_db.Products p ON st.ProductID = p.ProductID WHERE st.Status = 'Open' GROUP BY p.ProductName ORDER BY OpenTicketCount DESC;

phases.goal: Generate the final report based on the query results.
